column5: ice will not be gone for 2 week on main lake.still ice in front of camp.horizontal bay maybe next week.still freezing at night tight to shore.walleye are in trout creek heavy.
I heard that Harris Bay was open and they say that you should be able to get to the main lake in a couple of days. I hope their right heading up there this weekend.
Any word on Ice around Trapper Point and in front of Rusty Myers?
ice is open in front of rusty.but not main lake.its snowing now about 2 inches on ground.need lots of wind
